Set writeback encoders as possible clones for DSI encoders and vice
versa.

Reviewed-by: Dmitry Baryshkov <dmitry.baryshkov@linaro.org>
Signed-off-by: Jessica Zhang <quic_jesszhan@quicinc.com>
